{"tid":558793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"於平台向放狗女神露械自瀆 男商人罪成獲准保釋","createTime":"2018-02-12T14:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T15:07:00.000Z","uid":30794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d0a6faac24122cd1127066c6ca89422655ccb2","tid":558793,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"24歲女子夜晚放狗途經油塘邨平台，遇上一名已婚瓷磚男商人，對方突然向她說「你好靚」後掏出陽具在她面前自瀆，女子致電男友求援，男友趕至並尾隨商人，又用電話拍片追捕。<span style=\"color: red;\">事後事主於fb發帖，自言「我太靚」、「唉我都想放低女神嘅包袱」。</span>男商人經審訊後今被裁定有違公德罪罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n被告譚德昭（34歲）於去年1月16日晚犯案，辯方求情指被告非有預謀犯案，亦不是如其他有違公德案般偷拍女性裙底，且犯案時間短，年近歲晚，望能保釋候判。裁判官索閱被告的感化及社會服務令報告，准他保釋至下月2日判刑，又警告被告有可能會被判監。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180212/57823047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F57823047&d=C4m1H2JqtdZvwNb6zD3JbWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=53805b69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F57823047&h=d7ba95db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180212/57823047</a>"},{"pid":"5aa2a56a5e69756a59188d4512b21b18faf4f6a5","tid":558793,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}